name: testErrorIsDisplayedWhenCreatingCompanyWithSpecialCharacters
description: Error is displayed when trying to create a company with special characters in the name.
descriptionHtml: Error is displayed when trying to create a company with special characters in the name.

steps.name: Enter the user's email in the 'Email' field
Enter the user's password in the 'Password' field

testStage.description: Error is displayed when trying to create a company with special characters in the name.

steps.name: Click on 'System administration' menu in Header
Fill company name field with the name: Company!
Fill company type field with the type: CompanyType
Click on the 'Create' button and trigger an error
Verify: error message is displayed about invalid characters in the company name
